Esse eh um projeto para explorar melhor a navegacao entre Fragments num app

Pretendo explorar metodos como popBackStack

Essa aplicacao inicia numa activity e o usuario pode acessar fragments atraves de botoes. Quero
saber como fazer para o usuario ficar indo e voltado entre fragments e activites, principalmente quando
ele pressiona o o botao back


Alguns discussoes sobre quando usar fragment e quando usar activities

https://www.reddit.com/r/androiddev/comments/2r1wcw/fragments_vs_activities/
https://stackoverflow.com/questions/20306091/dilemma-when-to-use-fragments-vs-activities
https://stackoverflow.com/questions/12978141/how-to-choose-activity-or-fragment-if-both-scenarios-are-possible
https://stackoverflow.com/questions/18885311/use-activity-or-fragment-in-android-application
https://stackoverflow.com/questions/10863572/programmatically-go-back-to-the-previous-fragment-in-the-backstack